{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8e6faa83eb","title":"关于绝食静坐的问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bbdd69d8ec","index":0,"year":1967,"month":6,"day":29,"articleId":"8e6faa83eb"}],"tags":[{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"56fc802eb7","name":"人民内部矛盾","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"},{"id":"maoquanji49","name":"毛泽东全集第49卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/49-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"50263371ef","type":"paragraph","text":"五、伟大的战无不胜的马克思列宁主义[毛泽东思想]万岁","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"},{"id":"425d87946a","type":"paragraph","text":"对姚文元同志纺间阿尔巴尼亚的指示","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"},{"id":"b3a7b95538","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年六月）这次出去要注意谦虚啊！这不是一个代表团的问题，而且关系到中国红卫兵问题。","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"},{"id":"172ed11822","type":"paragraph","text":"关于超食静坐的间题","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"},{"id":"2f2dd2de86","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年六月二十九日）","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"},{"id":"e018d358fd","type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义制度下，无产阶级专政条件下，绝食解坐可以做为一种斗争手段。因为无产阶级内部有一小摄敌人，有官擦主义。他无非要让你答应几个条件。所以绝食静坐，允许。但不能提倡，一般不赞成。绝食可以开水放糖、放盐、打葡萄糖，可以轮班。","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"},{"id":"4c78482b6b","type":"paragraph","text":"看了西安师院造反派两张大字报","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"},{"id":"1be4595451","type":"paragraph","text":"和给中央交革的信后的批示","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"},{"id":"829fb6b29a","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年六月）","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"},{"id":"43ef73f816","type":"paragraph","text":"现在有的人是“铺张革命”，“大少爷作风”，“掌权开始，是浪费开始。”如果是人民内部矛盾的，批评人家宽一些，批评自己严一些。","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"},{"id":"7d5651c8e3","type":"paragraph","text":"关于新甸间题的指示","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"},{"id":"081b6b7783","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年七月一日）细甸问题不怕断交，不怕决裂，甚至于这个时候断交更好，这样更有利于我们放开手干。","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"},{"id":"925edde444","type":"paragraph","text":"关于建造主席塑象周题的指示","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"},{"id":"8938c0a91a","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年七月五日）林彪、恩来及文革小组各同志此类事是劳民伤财，无利有害，如不制止，势必会刮起一阵浮夸风。碰头会讨论一下发一指示，加以制止。","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"},{"id":"53a590cf98","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"},{"id":"993af4fc05","type":"paragraph","text":"七月五日","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"},{"id":"664015f064","type":"paragraph","text":"·317","index":16,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"}],"page":{"id":"9fea513bf2","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"8e6faa83eb","start":330,"end":330}},"maoquanji49":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8c249882be","type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义制度下，无产阶级专政条件下，绝食静坐可以作为一种斗争手段。因为无产阶级内部有一小操敌人，有官主义。他无非要让你答应几个条件。所以绝食静坐，允许，但不能提倡，一般不赞成。绝食可以开水放糖、放盐、打葡萄糖，可以轮班。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"},{"id":"fe2b63177f","type":"title","text":"关于绝食静坐的问题","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"8e6faa83eb"}],"page":{"id":"1c81455c37","publicationId":"maoquanji49","articleId":"8e6faa83eb","start":510,"end":510}}}},"__N_SSG":true}